    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/0276bb2bc9765a052c5fdebf5edd095f.poster.avif?t=1728418705\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/0276bb2bc9765a052c5fdebf5edd095f.webm?t=1728418705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/4c1180b7ea7ce95104caf1509885ea8c.webp?t=1728418705\" width=600 height=32 /></span><br><br>Trophy Knight is a Metroid style action platformer. Part treasure hunt, part noble adventure story, our hero is on a journey to find and defeat the ultimate foe. Guided by some mysterious voices, he will travel far and wide on a quest for redemption.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/93336aedfa0505ad78c157d118d14846.poster.avif?t=1728418705\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/93336aedfa0505ad78c157d118d14846.webm?t=1728418705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/4c1180b7ea7ce95104caf1509885ea8c.webp?t=1728418705\" width=600 height=32 /></span><br>After each successful boss fight, the player gets to pick up a trophy and bring it back to the trophy room for all to admire. But it is not always easy to navigate those narrow dungeon corridors when your hands are full. Definitely watch your head and mind the gap.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/d424642018581411efd4af69b7987514.poster.avif?t=1728418705\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/d424642018581411efd4af69b7987514.webm?t=1728418705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/4c1180b7ea7ce95104caf1509885ea8c.webp?t=1728418705\" width=600 height=32 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic pixel art side scrolling action and adventure.<br></li><li>Exquisite environments with smooth parallax and lighting effects.<br></li><li>Explore ancient ruins, desolate lands and deep dungeons.<br></li><li>Fight epic bosses and put them on display in your trophy room.<br></li><li>Collect and upgrade new weapons.<br></li><li>Level up to fight even epic-er bosses!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/e42c4a4de4e961701566a75e242690cf.poster.avif?t=1728418705\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142890/extras/e42c4a4de4e961701566a75e242690cf.webm?t=1728418705\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
